FBIS4-60895 "drsov084_b_94025" FBIS-SOV-94-084 Daily Report 29 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Bragin Appointed Deputy Minister of Culture Bragin Appointed Deputy Minister of Culture LD2904162394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1309 GMT 29 Apr 94 LD2904162394 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Moscow April 29 TASS -- Vyacheslav Bragin, former head of the Ostankino Radio and Television Broadcasting Company, has been appointed deputy minister of culture of the Russian Federation. ITAR-TASS received an instruction of Russian Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin to that effect on Friday.
